Package dog.giraffe.image

Interface Image

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Log
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ImageReader
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BufferedImageReader, Cluster1, Cluster2, FileImageReader, Hue, HyperHue, Image.Abstract, Image.Transform, Intensity, Normalize, NormalizedDifferenceVegetationIndex, NormalizedHyperHue, Select
    public interface Image
extends Log
    An image is a rectangle of vectors. The main operation supported by an image is reading its contents line by line.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      static class  Image.Abstract
      Implementation of some trivial methods.
      static interface  Image.Reader
      A Reader contains all information to read a line of the image.
      static class  Image.Transform
      A Image.Transform is an image which performs some operation on a line read before returning it to the caller.
